headline: DEWALT® Debuts DEWALT TOUGHWIRE™ Cable Hanger System and New Trade Solutions at AHR Expo
summary: DEWALT, a Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) brand and leader in total jobsite solutions, today announced the launch of DEWALT TOUGHWIRE™, a cable hanger system for HVAC, sheet metal, electrical and plumbing applications. Debuting at this year's AHR Expo in Orlando, the system, made up of over 50 different components, offers a variety of strong, fast and easy suspension solutions designed for improving efficiency and simplifying installations for HVACR professionals.
